.Sh NAME
.Nm mnm
.Nd search messages using notmuch query
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar search-term
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
uses
.Xr notmuch-search 1
to search mail, with
.Ar search-term
as the query.
.sp
The output is a list of filenames, one per line, suitable for piping to other
.Xr mblaze 7
utilities.
.sp
See
.Xr notmuch-search-terms 7
for the query syntax.
